{
  "texts": [
    "Breast cancer is one of the most common malignant tumors in women worldwide 1, 2.",
    "Nursing care plays an important role in patient recovery 1, 3.",
    "Traditionally, consultations with specialized nursing teams in hospitals have provided the most precise information; however, this approach is not always convenient to implement.",
    "With advances in artificial intelligence, generative large language models (LLMs) have shown significant promise in nursing 4, 5.",
    "Technologies such as ChatGPT are versatile, comprehensive, and intelligent, and can operate around the clock without fatigue."
  ]
}